\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Warmup-to-L ratio by case. Longer NRC service-life cases are flagged as higher initialization risk; this risk is review-required but not blocking because identity checks pass.}}{5}{figure.4}\protected@file@percent }
